Sybil Jason https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sybil_Jason 0 Sybil Jason (born Sybil Jacobson; 23 November 1927 – 23 August 2011) was a South African-born American child film actress who, in the late 1930s, was presented as a rival to Shirley Temple.
